==Ojibwe==
===ᐴᑭᒋᔥ (''boogijizh'')===

====Etymology====
# [[boogid|ᐴᑭᑦ (''boogid'')]]
# -yiN- (''vii'' to ''vta'' transformation suffix)
# transformation of terminal -N- to -zh

====Animate object transitive verb====
# [[fart]] at SB
# [[spray]] at SB (as what a [[skunk]] does)

====Transformations====
*unaffected: ᐴᑭᒋᔥ (''boogijizh'')
**unaffected with syncope: ᐴ<sup>ᑭ</sup>ᒋᔥ (''boogjizh'')
*initial change: ᑆᑭᒋᔥ (''bwaagijizh'')
**initial change with syncope: ᑆ<sup>ᑭ</sup>ᒋᔥ (''bwaagjizh'')
*reduplication: ᐹᐴᑭᒋᔥ (''baaboogijizh'')
**reduplication with syncope: ᐹᐴ<sup>ᑭ</sup>ᒋᔥ (''baaboogijizh'')
*initial change reduplication: ᐹᐹᐴᑭᒋᔥ (''baabaaboogijizh'')
**initial change reduplication with syncope: ᐹᐹᐴ<sup>ᑭ</sup>ᒋᔥ (''baabaaboogijizh'')

